member.example:
This sample shows how to call CompleteAsync with required parameters and parse the result.

var credential = new DefaultAzureCredential();
var client = new DiscoveriesClient(credential);

var operation = await client.CompleteAsync(WaitUntil.Completed, "<discoveryId>");

BinaryData data = await operation.WaitForCompletionAsync();
JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(data.ToStream()).RootElement;
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("operationId").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("status").ToString());

This sample shows how to call CompleteAsync with all parameters, and how to parse the result.

var credential = new DefaultAzureCredential();
var client = new DiscoveriesClient(credential);

var operation = await client.CompleteAsync(WaitUntil.Completed, "<discoveryId>", "<operationId>");

BinaryData data = await operation.WaitForCompletionAsync();
JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(data.ToStream()).RootElement;
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("operationId").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("status").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("operationType").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("error").GetProperty("code").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("error").GetProperty("message").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("error").GetProperty("target").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("error").GetProperty("innererror").GetProperty("code").ToString());

member.remarks:
Below is the JSON schema for the response payload.

Response Body:

Schema for DiscoveryLroResponse:
{
  operationId: string, # Required.
  status: "Created" | "InProgress" | "Succeeded" | "Failed" | "Canceled", # Required.
  operationType: "CompleteDiscovery" | "FinalizeFileList" | "AbortDiscovery", # Optional.
  error: {
    code: string, # Required.
    message: string, # Required.
    target: string, # Optional.
    details: [Error], # Required.
    innererror: {
      code: string, # Required.
      innererror: InnerError, # Optional.
    }, # Optional.
  }, # Optional.
}

